{"tid":1105223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人屋企冇房","createTime":"2019-04-13T17:26:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T18:47:26.000Z","uid":247639,"like":32,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3174c52262d64f6236906394d5355a6fbe524220","tid":1105223,"uid":247639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:26:07.000Z","msg":"我好想有間房呀屌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有房= 有私隱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇房=冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2082cd42e1424efbfd8756fc333b5a79ab6b92","tid":1105223,"uid":104502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:28:09.000Z","msg":"自己床都無"},{"pid":"ad1604d1c02cebabcfed05f7ff3580d841bf1bd1","tid":1105223,"uid":247639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e2082cd42e1424efbfd8756fc333b5a79ab6b92","tid":1105223,"uid":104502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:28:09.000Z","msg":"自己床都無"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:30:36.000Z","msg":"你搞笑？"},{"pid":"b7947bdf987c353b22d5f843ed77cac18c755185","tid":1105223,"uid":225760,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:42:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b0e447a4348de74613266b75a6712eb82884cf4","tid":1105223,"uid":174763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:55:17.000Z","msg":"有，由細到大屋企都冇房，我自己訓屋企近門口嗰邊，老豆老母訓屋企最入面嗰邊，然後用個衣櫃隔住咗，平時就咁係見唔到老豆老母個位，就好似分咗兩個空間咁。但佢哋要出門或者去廚房基本上就會見到我個空間，其實好冇私隱。然後我就咁就渡過咗我嘅童年同中學生捱。<br />\n<br />\n不過呢啲都係過去了，半年前去咗澳洲住大屋，終於有屬於自己間房了。喺其他地方住過大屋，真係唔想翻香港住納米房，根本係K型社會。"},{"pid":"5a95d1e690357010b729970e7ad80fb2d4927be1","tid":1105223,"uid":238752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:55:22.000Z","msg":"訓廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11eb5a7efdc19b545d27b416416a7f53aee02cb7","tid":1105223,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:00:00.000Z","msg":"我同細妹老豆老母訓主人房<br />\n好彩夠位擺兩張碌架床<br />\n遲啲暑期裝修會喺廳間返間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac6309a572e8554fd967f0f9c4943b8393ff000","tid":1105223,"uid":19967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:02:40.000Z","msg":"25歲前都係冇房瞓廳<br />\n直到阿哥家姐結婚搬走哂<br />\n屋企又裝修埋先有間房 仲要係大房"},{"pid":"b32f991e53f19e5f0a1eda174f9c40d7b133d2ee","tid":1105223,"uid":104502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad1604d1c02cebabcfed05f7ff3580d841bf1bd1","tid":1105223,"uid":247639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e2082cd42e1424efbfd8756fc333b5a79ab6b92","tid":1105223,"uid":104502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:28:09.000Z","msg":"自己床都無"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:30:36.000Z","msg":"你搞笑？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:06:43.000Z","msg":"好撚出奇？"},{"pid":"02db1b53d15d518662e5f2802fbb910ccec430f6","tid":1105223,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:25:29.000Z","msg":"有房冇門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚反智<br />\n趟門永遠都唔閂 得簾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb04e21ec16d3f7e02d551d1d3530f8e21dee1bd","tid":1105223,"uid":34757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:26:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4894e0353e6609ec0990e75ae2d1d264640475f6","tid":1105223,"uid":129011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:47:26.000Z","msg":"總好過要同人share一間房 訓上下格床"}]}